Package task2

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    task2
    This class is responsible for bank simulation it following class members: HashMap bankBalance that holds the id and balance of every single bank HashMap loanerInfo that holds the id of the banks that loaned from us and the amount loaned HashMap obj holds an id of each bank and a hashmap that holds a map of values with ids and amounts of banks that borrowed money from a specific bank integer m_limit that holds the limit for balance integer m_numOfBanks that holds the number of banks that we're simulating
    task2_tester
    This program is a simulation of Banks.
